statements: SELECT * FROM spare_parts_inventory ORDER BY part_name ASC;
SELECT part_name, part_category, part_quantity FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE part_quantity > 10 ORDER BY part_quantity DESC;
SELECT part_name, part_unit_price FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE part_category = 'Engine Parts';
SELECT part_name, part_location FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE part_quantity BETWEEN 5 AND 20 ORDER BY part_quantity ASC;
SELECT part_id, part_name, part_unit_price FROM spare_parts_inventory ORDER BY part_unit_price DESC, part_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE part_quantity > 100 ORDER BY part_name ASC;
SELECT part_name, part_category, part_unit_price FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE part_category = 'Electrical' ORDER BY part_unit_price DESC;
SELECT part_id, part_name, part_quantity, part_location FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE part_quantity < 50 AND part_category LIKE 'Engine%' ORDER BY part_location ASC;
SELECT part_name, part_category, part_unit_price FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE part_name LIKE '%bolt%' AND part_unit_price < 30;
SELECT part_id, part_name, part_quantity, part_location FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE part_location IN ('Warehouse A', 'Warehouse B') ORDER BY part_quantity DESC, part_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts;
SELECT part_name, quantity FROM spare_parts WHERE price > 50;
SELECT device_name, location FROM devices WHERE device_type = 'smartphone';
SELECT * FROM devices ORDER BY device_name DESC;
SELECT device_name, location, device_type FROM devices WHERE location = 'Warehouse' AND device_type LIKE 'laptop%';
SELECT * FROM spare_parts WHERE quantity > 10 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT part_name, price FROM spare_parts WHERE quantity < 5;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts WHERE part_name ILIKE 'engine%' AND price >= 500;
SELECT device_name, COUNT(device_id) AS device_count FROM devices GROUP BY device_name ORDER BY device_count DESC;
SELECT device_name, location FROM devices WHERE device_type = 'laptop' OR device_type = 'tablet' ORDER BY location ASC;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts;
SELECT part_name, quantity FROM spare_parts WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT location, part_name FROM spare_parts ORDER BY location ASC;
SELECT device_name, manufacturer FROM devices WHERE manufacturer='Sony';
SELECT * FROM maintenance_logs WHERE technician_name='John Doe';
SELECT part_name, quantity FROM spare_parts WHERE quantity > 10 ORDER BY part_name ASC;
SELECT device_name, manufacturer FROM devices WHERE manufacturer = 'Samsung' ORDER BY manufacturer, device_name DESC;
SELECT part_name, quantity, location FROM spare_parts WHERE location LIKE '%Room%' ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM maintenance_logs WHERE maintenance_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-28' ORDER BY maintenance_date;
SELECT m.log_id, m.technician_name, d.device_name FROM maintenance_logs AS m JOIN devices AS d ON m.device_id = d.device_id ORDER BY m.log_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM SparePartsInventory;
SELECT part_name, quantity FROM SparePartsInventory WHERE location='Warehouse';
SELECT device_name, device_type FROM Devices ORDER BY device_name DESC;
SELECT part_name, quantity FROM SparePartsInventory WHERE quantity > 10 ORDER BY quantity ASC;
SELECT record_id, maintenance_date, technician_name, details FROM MaintenanceRecords WHERE maintenance_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM MaintenanceRecords WHERE technician_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT part_name, quantity FROM SparePartsInventory WHERE location LIKE '%Warehouse%';
SELECT d.device_name, dp.part_id, s.part_name FROM Devices d JOIN DevicePartsMap dp ON d.device_id = dp.device_id JOIN SparePartsInventory s ON dp.part_id = s.part_id WHERE d.device_type = 'Laptop';
SELECT m.record_id, m.maintenance_date, d.device_name, m.technician_name FROM MaintenanceRecords m JOIN Devices d ON m.device_id = d.device_id WHERE m.maintenance_date >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT s.part_name, s.quantity, d.device_name, d.device_type FROM SparePartsInventory s JOIN DevicePartsMap dp ON s.part_id = dp.part_id JOIN Devices d ON dp.device_id = d.device_id WHERE s.quantity > 10 AND d.device_type = 'Printer';
SELECT * FROM SpareParts;
SELECT part_name, quantity FROM SpareParts WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT device_id, device_name, location FROM Devices ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT log_id, maintenance_date, maintenance_type, technician FROM MaintenanceLogs WHERE maintenance_type='Routine';
SELECT technician_name, specialization FROM Technicians WHERE experience_years > 5;
SELECT part_name, quantity, location FROM SpareParts;
SELECT device_name, location, last_maintenance_date FROM Devices ORDER BY last_maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT t.technician_name, t.specialization, t.experience_years, m.maintenance_date FROM Technicians t INNER JOIN MaintenanceLogs m ON t.technician_name = m.technician;
SELECT d.device_name, dp.quantity, p.part_name FROM Devices d INNER JOIN DeviceParts dp ON d.device_id = dp.device_id INNER JOIN SpareParts p ON dp.part_id = p.part_id ORDER BY dp.quantity ASC;

SELECT d.device_name, m.maintenance_type, t.technician_name FROM Devices d LEFT JOIN MaintenanceLogs m ON d.device_id = m.device_id LEFT JOIN Technicians t ON m.technician = t.technician_name WHERE m.maintenance_type = 'Repair' ORDER BY d.device_name ASC;
